  <arrangement id="aspace_99f223ba96587ada960897032cccf4fb">
    <head>Arrangement</head>
<p>Folders are arranged chronologically within series.</p><p>The files are grouped into 3 series:</p><p>Series I: City Council Meetings, 1889-1904</p><p>Series II: City Clerk - Correspondence, 1897-1906</p><p>Series III: Tax Anticipation Notes, 1933</p>  </arrangement>
